  "texts": [
    "There was a clear indication that patients were satisfied using these platforms in terms of high levels of reported satisfaction and corresponding improvements in diseasespecific assessment metrics.",
    "Our fidings also indicated a paucity of research focused specifically on the evaluation of the effectiveness of integrating AI with VRehab for patients in their homes.",
    "Reporting VRehab characteristics.",
    "Most of the reviewed studies reported baseline demographic information of patients 67, 68, such as age, sex, medical condition or diagnosis, comorbidity, marital status, employment status, income, socioeconomic status, and health insurance coverage.",
    "However, barriers influencing patient adherence to both in-person and VRehab programs were not reported including 2, 69: transportation issues, family obligations, lack of motivation and energy, and finding rehabilitation exercises tiring and painful."
  ]
}